reviewText: Good basic techniques, easy to follow.  I also have her DVD that uses hand weights and uses belly dance moves which I love.
This video was recommended by my instructor who knows Anja.  They both teach the same way so it was easy for me to follow and practice with on days when I am alone
I use this often. It is good for a quick workout, uses dance and weights and gives you a good mix of both.
Anja is sweet, and I like this dvd.  I was able to get it at Ross for $5.99, and it was well worth the price.
